      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-8 portfolio-item">
        <h3>LOSE Weight and get paid doing it</h3>
        <p>Losing weight is hard. And the more you have to lose, the harder it is. After three weeks of fasting, it is just too tempting to celebrate the progress you've made during the past three weeks by treating yourself to a piece of cheesecake or the delicious burger you've been keeping at a safe distance.</p>
