        <p>We help you reach a healthy Body Mass Index (BMI) in a fun and innovative way. Here's how it works:</p>
        <p>
        <ol>
          <li>You tell us your <strong>current weight and height</strong> and we'll tell you your current BMI. You should only use our service if you're overweight.</li>
          <li>You tell us <strong>how much money you want to bet</strong> each week on your own progress. This sum defines how much you'll have to pay to the community pot if you fail to loose weight in a week. It also defines how big your share of the weekly payout will be when you reach your goal and lose weight.</li>
          <li>Every monday we'll ask you to upload <strong>a fresh picture of your scale</strong> via the <a href="http://evernote.com" target="_blank">Evernote App</a>. We'll automatically read your current weight and keep it in a log book for you.</li>
          <li><strong>We help you work towards a healthy BMI</strong> by providing you with delicious but healthy recipes - delivered directly to your <a href="http://evernote.com" target="_blank">Evernote Notebook</a> including a shopping list - so that you always have the list at your finger tips when you go shopping.</li>
