            <p>Also, if you reach a healthy BMI - anything between 18.5 and 24.9 â€“ you can quit at any time. We also don't want you to drop below 18.5 and we'll automatically suggest to eat more if you get too close to the lower threshold and update your shopping list. Of course, we'll not charge you anything as long as you stay within these bounds.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Can I export my data?</strong></p>
            <p>Yes, we'll soon add support to export your data to <%= link_to "Evernote", "http://www.evernote.com" %> notebooks.</p>
